Filter
   The expression in this box displays which directories and files will be listed in the Directories and Files Boxes below it.  You can change the expression by clicking in the window and typing.  To show a list of the directories and files at the location of your new expression, click on the Filter button at the bottom of the Rotation File Selection Window.

Directories
   This box displays the directories found in the current location specified by the Filter Box.  Double-clicking on particular directories will change the filter expression to that new directory.  In particular, double-clicking on the .. directory will select the directory right before the current directory.  Scroll bars are also present if the directory names don't fit inside the box.

